OL,3,CReform mayor Luke Campbell rules out
OL,4,Ctourist tax
OL,6,FReform's mayor for Hull and East
OL,7,FYorkshire has ruled out imposing a
OL,8,F"tourist tax" following Rachel Reeves'
OL,9,Fbudget.
OL,11,FThe Chancellor announced that regional
OL,12,Fmayors would be given the power to add
OL,13,Fa "modest" charge - thought to be
OL,14,Faround #2 a night - to the cost of
OL,15,Fovernight accommodation to fund local
OL,16,Fservices.
OL,18,FBut Luke Campbell said that, while the
OL,19,Flevy could bring in extra cash, it
OL,20,Fwould be the "wrong decision" for the
OL,21,Fregion.
