OL,3,CReform mayor Luke Campbell rules out
OL,4,Ctourist tax
OL,6,F"I think it's just another tax and I
OL,7,Fthink people are paying enough taxes,"
OL,8,Fhe said.
OL,10,F"We'd all love the extra pennies (but)
OL,11,Fwe need to promote tourism and
OL,12,Fincrease it and I think by adding a
OL,13,Ftourism levy we'll do the opposite."
OL,15,FMr Campbell's region includes coastal
OL,16,Fdestinations like Bridlington, along
OL,17,Fwith the historic market town of
OL,18,FBeverley and the city of Hull.
