OL,6,FAccording to Visit Hull and East
OL,7,FYorkshire, the region welcomed 12.1
OL,8,Fmillion visitors in 2023, generating
OL,9,Fmore than #815million for the area.
OL,11,FThe tourist tax has been backed by
OL,12,Fother mayors including Labour's Andy
OL,13,FBurnham in Greater Manchester and
OL,14,FTracy Brabin in West Yorkshire.
OL,16,FMs Brabin said at the time of the
OL,17,Fannouncement: "This will allow us to
OL,18,Finvest more into making our regions
OL,19,Feven better places to visit, unlocking
OL,20,Fopportunities and help our businesses
OL,21,Fthrive."
