OL,3,CReform mayor Luke Campbell rules out
OL,4,Ctourist tax
OL,6,FDestinations like Paris, New York and
OL,7,FMilan already charge a similar levy.
OL,9,FBut former boxing champion Mr Campbell
OL,10,Fsaid the tax would "put a lot of
OL,11,Fstress and pain on businesses" and
OL,12,Fthat "it's the opposite to what growth
OL,13,Fshould be".
OL,15,FHis reservations have been backed by
OL,16,Fsome hospitality providers.
