OL,4,Ctourist tax
OL,6,FStefan Micevski, chair of the
OL,7,FHospitality Association in York -
OL,8,Fwhere Labour mayor David Skaith
OL,9,Fwelcomed the announcement - said
OL,10,Fbusinesses were "worried" about what
OL,11,Fthe levy would mean.
OL,13,F"It adds up for the guest's bill," he
OL,14,Ftold ITV Calendar, adding that surveys
OL,15,Fwere already suggesting consumers were
OL,16,Fspending less on overnight stays.
OL,18,FHe said: "The consumers are very price
OL,19,Fconscious, so adding one or two pounds
OL,20,Fadditional to their bill will not
OL,21,Fincrease the visitors per year."
