OL,3,CReform mayor Luke Campbell rules out
OL,4,Ctourist tax
OL,6,FMr Campbell, who was elected in May,
OL,7,Fhas already diverged from his party on
OL,8,Fsome policies, including green energy
OL,9,Fand Northern Powerhouse Rail.
OL,11,FHe added: "I actually don't think that
OL,12,Fthe mayor's role is that political,
OL,13,Fbecause it's always place based."
OL,15,F"Hull and East Yorkshire has been left
OL,16,Fbehind for a long time now...I think
OL,17,Fthis region has the potential to be
OL,18,Fone of the best in the country."
